{"tid":831451,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今年美心冰皮好食過大班多多聲","createTime":"2018-09-22T03:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T06:37:24.000Z","uid":150912,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bb12734ba5248fdce261a09c39ec2ca70e8a0618","tid":831451,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"大班冰皮永遠陣好微的腥味   其他果味有時會似藥水 而且冇咩香味<br />\n今年美心完全冇依個問題<br />\n而且任何味都好好食<br />\n綠豆好滑好潤  <br />\n其他都好出色<br />\n特別係荔枝 朱古力脆脆 芝麻 芒果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱古力脆脆入面真係有脆粒粒  冇軟到 朱古力味亦都算濃<br />\n芝麻冰皮超香  食哂成個仲有香味留係鼻到<br />\n最估唔到係荔枝 可以整得咁香甜而冇藥水味 真係似返一種生果甜品<br />\n芒果唔洗講基本上唔會衰<br />\n每次食都係成個啪  <br />\n唔似大班只係食到少少之後放返入盒俾下個食<br />\n<br />\n依家食完盒美心冰皮 有少少想買盒榴連冰皮返黎試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1e1d3b9fb10672f1a15411585080a05b678e59","tid":831451,"uid":184108,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e9027959b7bb6307a08d57e7e5ab56955e90e7b","tid":831451,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d1e1d3b9fb10672f1a15411585080a05b678e59","tid":831451,"uid":184108,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:19:11.000Z","msg":"你都on9<br />\n我邊忽有賣券"},{"pid":"41b5d5111b45812d820b8df90d4892454785c2f1","tid":831451,"uid":150912,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d1e1d3b9fb10672f1a15411585080a05b678e59","tid":831451,"uid":184108,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"而且我拎黎炒/散貨的話<br />\n出街俾車撞死<br />\n如果唔係你死全家"},{"pid":"3c68df277d3fe28e0a57df9c887c6c0e220a53c3","tid":831451,"uid":70754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:24:07.000Z","msg":"打手是狗"},{"pid":"9a840fe27fa4aa2dffeb33018f9f803d47acece6","t